# Current Goal

Build the complete desktop companion before investing heavily in production electronics.

The first hardware prototype is intentionally simple.

Prototype Hardware:

ESP32-S3

OLED Display

Speaker

Microphone

2 Servos

USB Communication

No large sensor cluster during MVP.

Sensors will be added after the desktop software is stable.

